data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a comfortable living space with a little over 1400 square feet. The interior features a light color palette, creating a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, enhancing the sense of space and promoting a modern and welcoming feel. The kitchen is equipped with a breakfast bar, providing a convenient spot for casual dining or entertaining guests. The bedrooms are well-proportioned, offering ample space for furniture and personalization. With two bathrooms, convenience and privacy are prioritized for the residents. The patio out back extends the living space outdoors, providing a perfect spot for relaxation, outdoor dining, or hosting gatherings. Overall, this home combines practicality with a stylish design, making it a cozy and inviting space for its occupants. Located just 17 minutes to Downtown Pensacola, and just 27 minutes to Pensacola Beach. Book your showing now !!
